title: LLMMMO
description: A text-based MMORPG where language mastery is your greatest weapon.
long_description: LLMMMO immerses players in a vast online world where communication drives action. Engage in quests, form alliances, and battle foes using text commands, emphasizing strategy and linguistic skill.
how_to_play: Navigate the game world by typing commands to interact with characters, objects, and other players. Success depends on clear and strategic communication.

title: AstroDash
description: Navigate your spaceship through treacherous asteroid fields at breakneck speeds.
long_description: AstroDash challenges players to pilot a spacecraft, dodging obstacles and collecting power-ups across procedurally generated space environments. Quick reflexes and precise control are essential to survive and achieve high scores.
how_to_play: Use arrow keys or touch controls to steer your ship, avoiding asteroids and collecting items to boost your score and survivability.

title: Necropolis: Rise of the Undead
description: Command an undead army to conquer the living and expand your dark empire.
long_description: In Necropolis, players assume the role of a necromancer, raising and commanding undead forces to battle human settlements. Strategic resource management and tactical combat are key to dominating the realm.
iframe_url: Necropolis: Rise of the Undead - Zombie FPS Game
how_to_play: Utilize mouse clicks or touch inputs to summon units, direct attacks, and manage resources. Balance offense and defense to overcome increasingly challenging enemies.

title: Neon Trailblazer
description: Illuminate the digital void by creating neon trails in a cybernetic landscape.
long_description: Neon Trailblazer combines fast-paced racing with puzzle elements. Players control a light-emitting vehicle, crafting paths to solve challenges and outmaneuver adversaries in a vibrant, neon-lit world.
how_to_play: Control your vehicle using WASD keys or swipe gestures, creating trails to complete puzzles and block opponents while avoiding collisions.

title: Bubble Basher
description: Pop, dodge, and bash your way through bubble mayhem.
long_description: Bubble Basher offers players a fun and frantic experience, requiring them to burst bubbles of various sizes and speeds before they overwhelm the screen. Power-ups and combos enhance the excitement.
how_to_play: Click or tap on bubbles to pop them, aiming for streaks to build combos. Utilize power-ups strategically to manage the increasing bubble influx.

title: Flight Simulator 2025
description: Experience the future of aviation with cutting-edge flight simulation technology.
long_description: Flight Simulator 2025 provides an ultra-realistic piloting experience, featuring next-gen aircraft, dynamic weather systems, and global navigation. Aspiring pilots can hone their skills in various scenarios and challenges.
how_to_play: Use a combination of keyboard controls and mouse inputs to operate the aircraft's systems, following on-screen prompts and tutorials to master takeoffs, flights, and landings.

title: Dogfight Arena
description: Engage in high-octane aerial combat against skilled pilots worldwide.
long_description: Dogfight Arena is a multiplayer flight combat game where players pilot fighter jets in intense dogfights. Customize your aircraft, execute tactical maneuvers, and climb the global leaderboard.
how_to_play: Control your jet using joystick or tilt controls, firing weapons and deploying countermeasures with designated buttons. Team coordination and sharp reflexes are vital for victory.

title: Type Battles
description: Outtype your opponents to unleash devastating attacks in this typing duel.
long_description: Type Battles transforms typing speed and accuracy into combat prowess. Players face off by typing words or phrases, with faster and more precise typists dealing greater damage to their adversaries.
iframe_url: Type Battles: Free Speed Typing Game
how_to_play: Type the prompted words or sentences as quickly and accurately as possible to attack your opponent. Mistakes reduce damage output, so precision is key.

title: Mars Landing Simulator
description: Master the art of landing spacecraft on the challenging Martian terrain.
long_description: Mars Landing Simulator tasks players with safely landing various spacecraft on Mars, accounting for gravity, wind, and surface conditions. Each mission increases in difficulty, testing piloting skills to the limit.
how_to_play: Adjust thrust and angle using on-screen controls to guide your lander to a safe touchdown, monitoring speed and fuel levels carefully.

title: The Agency
description: Navigate a world of espionage and intrigue as an elite secret agent.
long_description: In The Agency, players undertake covert missions, utilizing stealth, gadgets, and combat skills to achieve objectives. Choices impact the storyline, leading to multiple endings.
